description: For mobile apps, do not use Tailwind CSS
globs: apps/{classic,ai-first}/**
alwaysApply: false
---

# Mobile Apps: No Tailwind CSS

- For `apps/classic` and `apps/ai-first`, do not use Tailwind CSS utilities or Tailwind-based styling patterns.
- Do not introduce new Tailwind dependencies, config usage, or utility-class refactors in mobile app code.
- Prefer CSS Modules, plain CSS, or the existing local styling approach already used in the target file/app.
- If a task explicitly asks for Tailwind, ask for confirmation before proceeding because this rule forbids it by default.
